        "content": "<p>You <em>may</em> be giving me too much credit by assuming I wouldn't be lured in by the same thing twice <span aria-label=\"wink\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f609\" role=\"img\" title=\"wink\">:wink:</span> </p>\n<p>(Somebody should vibe code up an \"(un)ordered list of links\" dupe checker)</p>",
